The mother of Yayaha Muhammad, a lawmaker in the Jigawa State House Assembly,  has been kidnapped by gunmen. This was confirmed by the Jigawa State Commissioner of Police, Bala Zama, confirmed this today (Tuesday). The lawmaker's mother was kidnapped Monday night from her residence in Danladin Gumel, Suletankarkar local council of the state. The National Youth Leader of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) was also kidnapped on Monday night on his farm in Enugu.